{{\b
Aims of the course: }}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{The course introduces fundamental conceptual and theoretical principles 
upon which the practice of marketing is based\'2e It is focused on 
definition of marketing, analysis of marketing environment, forms 
of marketing research, segmentation and targeting, brand and brand 
positioning, marketing mix and on marketing planning\'2e All principles 
are applied to diverse sectors \_ to consumer goods and services, 
B2B markets, non\_profit organizations etc\'2e \line
}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{\~}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{{\b
Learning outcomes and competences: }}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{Upon successful completion of this course, students will be able to:\line
\_ explain the fundamental marketing principles;\line
\_ characterize the basic marketing strategies, models, methods, concepts 
and tools;\line
\_ apply basic marketing strategies, methods, and tools;\line
\_ create, present, and defend a simple marketing plan for a given 
product;\line
\_ realize a simple marketing research;\line
\_ discuss the societal effects of marketing\'2e}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{\~}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{{\b
