}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{1\'2e Marketing, marketing concept and market orientation \line
2\'2e Marketing micro environment and macro environment \line
3\'2e Marketing research \line
4\'2e Segmentation and targeting \line
5\'2e Brand and brand positioning \line
6\'2e Marketing mix: product \line
7\'2e Marketing mix: price \line
8\'2e Marketing mix: communication  \line
9\'2e Marketing mix: convenience \line
10\'2eMarketing planning \line
11\'2eThe role of marketing in companies \line
}\cell\row\pard
